.Nm
is a curses Klondike solitaire game.
.Pp
The keys are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Ic q
Quit.
.It Ic u
Undo.
.It Ic space
Draw from stock to waste.
.It Ic w
Select waste.
.It Ic a-d
Select foundation.
.It Ic 1-7
Select tableau.
.It Ic enter
Move to any foundation.
